## Important Rules

1. ✅ Optimize LCP: optimized images, critical content first
2. ✅ Minimize CLS: explicit dimensions, placeholders
3. ✅ Reduce FID: minimal JavaScript, defer scripts
4. ✅ Use Astro's `<Image>` for all images
5. ✅ Load data in parallel with `Promise.all()`
6. ✅ Use streaming SSR for progressive content
7. ✅ Minimize JavaScript sent to client
8. ✅ Optimize DB queries (avoid N+1)
9. ✅ Use appropriate cache (browser, CDN)
10. ✅ Monitor Web Vitals in production
